page.title: 04FLORA,FAUNA AROUND REETH
page.content: Amelia,Emma,Alexandra,Paul,and John.We have made a list of the flowers,trees,birds, and animals that we think are representative of our area. {Flowers:}Primroses,bluebells,small red orchid,wood sorrell,kingcup,wild garlic,wild thyme,cranesbill,dog roses,willow herb,heartsease,campion. {Trees:}Ash,elm,(suffering from Dutch Elm Disease)rowan,alder,willow,larch,junip er(protected)holly, {Birds:}Red grouse,lapwing,curlew,heron,dipper,wag tails,pheasants,gulls, {Animals:}Rabbits,hedgehog,roe deer,weasel,stoats,fox,hare.
